data.description: Located in a Cozy Community close to Downtown, this home is wonderful for any family to make it their own. Don't let the current condition of this property fool you.  Imagine breathing new life into this home by financing your dream upgrades into your home loan!  Features: 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, fireplace, kitchen w/ beautiful wood cabinets and granite countertops. A trellis is a great addition to your future garden.
